						               													<description>Base is a strategic, abstract puzzle game with a unique worker placement bid mechanism.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Grab modules and build your base! The goal of the game is to build as many rows and columns of 5 modules into your base following the given building instructions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To get the necessary modules, you have to send trading delegations to neighbouring planets. As your fellow players will do the same, you should wisely choose the size of your delegation because size matters when it comes to trade negotiations. For each row or column that you accomplish within a round, you earn instant points that give you special actions. After 6 rounds, the game ends.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Now it&amp;rsquo;s time to score the secret side contracts that each of you signed with the private sector. The player with the most points wins the game and gets governor of his own planet.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
